    "description": "Solara Active Pharma, one of India's leading organizations, is hiring a Radiologist for our Ghaziabad operations. We offer a competitive salary package along with world-class benefits.\n\nAbout Solara Active Pharma:\nSolara Active Pharma is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Conduct routine health assessments and screenings\n• Respond to medical emergencies and provide immediate care\n• Collaborate with pharmaceutical representatives and medical suppliers\n• Participate in quality improvement initiatives and clinical audits\n• Diagnose and treat medical conditions following established protocols\n• Administer medications and treatments as prescribed\n• Educate patients and families on health management and disease prevention\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Diploma or Degree in Hospitality Management\n• 10-15 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Clinical Documentation\n• Proficiency in Diagnostic Skills\n• Proficiency in Medical Ethics\n• Proficiency in EMR/EHR\n• Proficiency in Infection Control\n• Proficiency in Medical Terminology\n• Proficiency in CPT Codes\n• Proficiency in BLS/ACLS\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Employee stock options (ESOPs) for eligible roles\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• International travel opportunities for senior roles\n• Salary Range: 20 LPA - 40 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Ghaziabad, Uttar Pradesh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Solara Active Pharma!",
